Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:38.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,♫Itu cuma luka gores♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,♫PAYA PAYA PAYA♫
