Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:17.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,♫Selamat ulang tahun, Choco♫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:22.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,♫Semoga terus senang dan riang selalu♫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:26.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,♫Selamat ulang tahun, Choco♫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lirik dan musik oleh Akagi Yuina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini hadiah dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dapat lagu orisinal\Ndi hari ulang tahun itu berat banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Liriknya bikin otakku serasa jadi bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:42.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, kalian berdua iri sama bakat aku, nih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagunya bagus, 'kan, Choco?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kerja keras biar\Nsemua orang sangat senang,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:52.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan kita bisa foto-foto emosional begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang itu terlalu berat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:54.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang kamu Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:55.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Choco?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, tiup lilinnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Jangan-jangan dia tidur?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kue cokelat bulat sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:13.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada dua kue bulat sempurna,\Nkhusus untuk Choco.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:17.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, maaf. Aku tiup sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu kebanyakan nangis, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Emosional bahagia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Kenapa kamu juga nangis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:30.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku senang banget dia senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuinacchoryn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:41.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senang ya, kita jadi merayakan ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:46.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, boleh aku bilang sekali lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:54.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:57.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
