Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke, sekarang kita foto bareng.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:33.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keroppe, tolong fotokan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:36.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keroppe tidak ikut difoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dingin banget, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:38.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:39.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke, semua kumpul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:41.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selfie bareng, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:48.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada pelanggan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:50.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tepat di waktu seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:55.08,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Jangan main-main denganku, Nenek.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:24:00.08,tanda-5,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1\bord0\shad4\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H80807E&\pos(546,734)}Selanjutnya
